import React from 'react';
import Helmet from '../components/Helmet';
import HeroSlider from '../components/HeroSlider';
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap';
import FindCarForm from '../components/FindCarForm';

import HotOffer from '../components/HotOffer';
import Testimonial from '../components/Testimonial';



import BecomeDriver from '../components/BecomeDriver';

import AboutSection from '../components/AboutSection';

const Home = () => {
    return ( <
        Helmet title = "Home" >
        <
        section className = "p-0 hero__slider__section" >
        <
        HeroSlider / >

        <
        div className = "hero__form" >
        <
        Container className = "" >
        <
        Row className = "form__row mx-0" >
        <
        Col lg = "4"
        md = "4" >
        <
        div className = "find__car__left" >
        <
        h2 > Search our best cars here < /h2> <
        /div> <
        /Col>

        <
        Col lg = "8"
        md = "8"
        sm = "12" >
        <
        FindCarForm / >
        <
        /Col> <
        /Row> <
        /Container> <
        /div> <
        /section>

        <
        section className = "about__section" >
        <
        Container >
        <
        AboutSection / >
        <
        /Container> <
        /section>



        <
        section >
        <
        Container >
        <
        Row >
        <
        Col lg = "12 text-center mb-5" >
        <
        h6 className = "section__subtitle" > Our Services < /h6> <
        h2 className = "section__title" > Cars in Available < /h2> <
        /Col>

        <
        HotOffer / >
        <
        /Row> <
        /Container> <
        /section>

        <
        section className = "become__driver" >
        <
        Container >
        <
        BecomeDriver / >
        <
        /Container> <
        /section>

        <
        section >
        <
        Container >
        <
        Row >
        <
        Col lg = "12"
        className = "text-center" >
        <
        h6 className = "section__subtitle" > Our Clients Says < /h6> <
        h2 className = "section__title" > Testimonial < /h2> <
        /Col>

        <
        Testimonial / >
        <
        /Row> <
        /Container> <
        /section>

        <
        /Helmet>
    );
};

export default Home;
